Else
    Commit
Endif


SI_TABLE = "XISOUFMFOU"
Gosub SI_CRITSUP From SIXFONCTION

Trbegin [XSFM]
For [XSFM] Where FLGREP<>2
&              & evalue(SI_CRITERE)

    Call AFFBOITE([XSFM]CODFAMFOU-[XSFM]CODSOUFAM) From SUBSIM

    Read [XFAM]IND0=[XSFM]CODFAMFOU
    If [F:XSFM]X3CLE<>"" & [XFAM]X3CLE<>""
        Call WRIADI(41, [F:XSFM]X3CLE, [XFAM]X3CLE, [F:XSFM]LIBSOUFAM, LRET)
